{"tid":2509482,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股票升到前高/破新高，如何部署？","createTime":"2021-04-29T12:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T13:11:55.000Z","uid":328235,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"69a4b799951e2e619879daf5b3b6b944c6420625","tid":2509482,"uid":328235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:43:24.000Z","msg":"新手買左幾隻疫苗股，升到前高/破新高，如何部署？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBNTX NVAX CVAC<br />\n其他股試過好幾次高位無走，坐左好耐貨，有心理陰影，但又試過早走賺少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剛開始學玩股票一個月，希望各位前輩屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f190051d70227a5191e9c9b47a9c0533f2216d","tid":2509482,"uid":130479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:55:03.000Z","msg":"大單流出 陰燭即走"},{"pid":"d0027ffd6000962b3d0bb2e4719cf5df9c31a48b","tid":2509482,"uid":134522,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"平時我見連登有好多人輸兩三成都可以 Strong Hold 到佢返家鄉，但係一到家鄉就放曬佢，真係好心痛。<br />\n<br />\n你既然覺得佢一定可以 Strong Hold 到家鄉，姐係你已經覺得佢係一間有價值、長揸穩陣既好公司，咁點解輸你夠膽 Strong Hold，贏你又唔敢 Strong Hold呢？<br />\n<br />\n朋友就話可以共富貴不可共患難，你買股票就偏偏只可以共患難唔可以共富貴？<br />\n<br />\n次次輸錢就 Strong Hold，贏錢就放，咁咪永遠只有坐艇沒有賺錢？最近依幾日科技股又升返啲，希望有緣人睇到可以悔改前非，見住咁多年輕人心理質素唔夠好賺唔到錢，真係櫈佢地唔抵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b56110bb110adc099f3221e0e49bb32f35624c","tid":2509482,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:58:09.000Z","msg":"贏谷輸縮"},{"pid":"4626389265f95a43feeca6f70eb6a218e5a2e7be","tid":2509482,"uid":53999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:58:55.000Z","msg":"分注走 無人可以最高點走 但如有信念咪渣住佢囉"},{"pid":"6f3373a102656edb0a5cec1397933e9ce5ccc25f","tid":2509482,"uid":175540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"賺少咗有咩問題?<br />\n最緊要唔好坐貨 <br />\n到時蝕價又浪費時間"},{"pid":"71268a028273513de5f5aec8a455bee9884ed890","tid":2509482,"uid":328235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0027ffd6000962b3d0bb2e4719cf5df9c31a48b","tid":2509482,"uid":134522,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"平時我見連登有好多人輸兩三成都可以 Strong Hold 到佢返家鄉，但係一到家鄉就放曬佢，真係好心痛。<br />\n<br />\n你既然覺得佢一定可以 Strong Hold 到家鄉，姐係你已經覺得佢係一間有價值、長揸穩陣既好公司，咁點解輸你夠膽 Strong Hold，贏你又唔敢 Strong Hold呢？<br />\n<br />\n朋友就話可以共富貴不可共患難，你買股票就偏偏只可以共患難唔可以共富貴？<br />\n<br />\n次次輸錢就 Strong Hold，贏錢就放，咁咪永遠只有坐艇沒有賺錢？最近依幾日科技股又升返啲，希望有緣人睇到可以悔改前非，見住咁多年輕人心理質素唔夠好賺唔到錢，真係櫈佢地唔抵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:02:19.000Z","msg":"TQQQ巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我買既大部分都係認真研究過，對前景有信心既股票（都有一兩隻妖股既）<br />\n但一開始學既時候買左幾隻，入既價位都好差，抄底又唔夠底，留下左陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外我怕大家都玩財伎，就算公司好都空死距<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚多野要學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cab3eee431134209835f632ce1d4bc1c375287","tid":2509482,"uid":328235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5f190051d70227a5191e9c9b47a9c0533f2216d","tid":2509482,"uid":130479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:55:03.000Z","msg":"大單流出 陰燭即走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:03:41.000Z","msg":"有咁簡單？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji